musicians.bio: Fun Fact: My roommate thinks that I’m like the Pillsburry doughboy; Desert Island Playlist: Bach, Brahms, Instrumental Pokémon music, Cross Game OST, MIKA, 李健, 李荣浩
Fun Fact: I’m a polyglot!; Desert Island Playlist: Forgotify for the memes, Classical, EDM, pop, etc.

Fun Fact: I'm really good at making omelettes; Desert Island Playlist: Brahms 4 (Kleiber/VPO), Abbey Road (Beatles), DAMN (Kendrick Lamar), Argerich's debut recital, Random Access Memories (Daft Punk), Bach Violin Sonatas/Partitas (Hilary Hahn)
Fun Fact: Absolutely love scuba diving; Desert Island Playlist: Mamma Mia Playlist
Fun Fact: I know the lyrics to the Eastern vs. Western Philosophers Epic Rap Battle of History by heart; Desert Island Playlist: conan gray, bulow, phildel, verite
Fun Fact: I used to drink and rate expensive water; Desert Island Playlist: Panic! At the Disco
Fun Fact: Master of peeling tangerines in spirals; Desert Island Playlist: math rock, early Jason Mraz, & ukulele instrumentals

Fun Fact: I once had a dream about how the quantum physics of light was related to the googly eyes on my alarm clock. It all made perfect sense until I woke up.; Desert Island Playlist: Bobby McFerrin's Medicine Music (?)
Fun Fact: I like to collect autographs.; Desert Island Playlist: Anime songs

Fun Fact: My right index finger is shorter than than my left one because I cut off my fingertip in an ice-skating accident when I was 5!; Desert Island Playlist: Beethoven String Quartets, the works of Tristan Murail, and Acid Rap!
Fun Fact: I once drank 19 Slurpees^TM in one day.; Desert Island Playlist: https://open.spotify.com/playlist/0osR8XPO06DWOI3pL0LVUA

Fun Fact: In third grade (a particularly petty time in my life), I got mad at my sister and wrote an entire book of poems making fun of her, filled with gems like “Anna is a dorky geek”; Desert Island Playlist: A mix of SZA, Lorde, Kendrick, and Prokofiev

Fun Fact: When I was a young child my dream careers were landscaper and professional squid catcher.; Desert Island Playlist: Tchaikovsky, Mendelssohn, Mozart, Schubert, Bill Evans, Gerry Mulligan, Art Blakey, Count Basie, and Charles Mingus

Fun Fact: My favorite cupcake flavor is strawberry!; Desert Island Playlist: Anything BTS (especially their old school albums and LY: Her)! Along with some Rex Orange County, Doja Cat, khai dreams and lots more!

Fun Fact: I played a private recital for Ruth Bader Ginsburg; Desert Island Playlist: The Well-Tempered Clavier, Art of Fugue, Mozart Piano Concertos, The Marriage of Figaro, The Magic Flute, Turangalîla Symphony, Javanese and Balinese Gamelan music
Fun Fact: I have a phobia of broken sprinklers!; Desert Island Playlist: My Broadway Musicals playlist on Spotify<3
Fun Fact: I have a cat named Owen; Desert Island Playlist: Lots of Beach House and Kanye West
Fun Fact: I prefer walking over biking!; Desert Island Playlist: Lots of heavy metal and punk music! Judas Priest, Iron Maiden, Discharge, Anti Cimex, etc.
